ên vân vạn thuỷ gian - 千雲萬水間</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-D%E1%BB%AF-C%E1%BA%A7u/Th%E1%BB%A9-T%E1%BA%B1ng-Ho%C3%A0nh-Ph%E1%BB%A5-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-EEgzwhtk78x82FpzPDpdxA">Thứ Tằng Hoành Phụ vận - 次曾宏父韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-D%E1%BB%AF-C%E1%BA%A7u/author-_upm8xz-TGTNsPiM9t-sIQ">Thẩm Dữ Cầu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%91i-Qu%E1%BB%B3nh/Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-Thi%E1%BA%BFt-Nhai-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-tu%C3%BD-ca/poem-zJHP1Nu_WXThiVc4VkIRqg">Thứ vận Thiết Nhai tiên sinh tuý ca - 次韻鐵崖先生醉歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%91i-Qu%E1%BB%B3nh/author-xiBFy5bXgpv8FC-1c8m5xA">Bối Quỳnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-S%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/Tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA/poem-J8jOZLmLUjaGID-yVZhfKg">Tuyệt cú - 絕句</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-S%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-xEsRxN5L9eDUR5ntEPNuXA">Trần Sư Đạo</a>)<br></div>	</div>
